			<div class="content" id="post-content-2475001">
									

<p>Yeah, sorry about that. The formatting for this document is pretty wonky. My goal was to try and replicate handwritten notes, but different browsers and devices tend to display it differently.</p>
<p>Originally, I was actually planning on handwriting these pages and uploading images. However, that never worked. I also realized it would be too hard to replicate, which was one of the stipulations for the contest (I realize that this is also hard to replicate, but I digress). So, this was actually my backup plan, and I suppose that it didn't quite work out either. But, with the time limit of the contest, I think it was as good as I could manage. I've never been good with HTML and CSS.</p>
<p>If I ever get enough free time to jump back in the site, my first goal will be to fix this. I've always wished it had turned out better. Unfortunately, I've been super busy recently and haven't had any time to devote to SCP. Hopefully that will change in the future, but only time will tell.</p>

